numix-gtk-themes (2016.03.17+variations1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Set source name to numix-gtk-themeS instead of numix-gtk-theme.
  * New upstream Git snapshots (as of 17 Mar 2016).
     - Numix Frost themes no longer provide a Cinnamon theme (this has
       been moved to a separate source).
  * Update debian/rules to compile Numix Frost themes with Sass.
  * Update copyright information to include the right year and authors.
  * Set standards version to 3.9.7.
  * Update GTK dependencies to >= 3.16.
  * Remove obsolete install and Lintian override files in debian/.

 -- James Lu <bitflip3@gmail.com>  Thu, 17 Mar 2016 22:50:28 -0700

